text: Fabián Saavedra Muñoz (born 27 January 1992) is a Chilean footballer who plays for the Primera División de Chile side Cobresal as a striker on loan from Unión Española. ==External links== *Besoccer profile * Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Chilean footballers Category:Association football forwards Category:Unión Española footballers Category:Santiago Morning footballers Category:Cobresal footballers Category:Chilean Primera División players Category:Primera B de Chile players
